Value isid (\d+)
Value bvlan (\d+)
Value system_name (.+)
Value system_bmac (([0-9A-Fa-f]{2}[:-]){5}([0-9A-Fa-f]){2})
Value multicast ((T|R|both)*)

Start
  ^Legend:\s+\*\s+indicates\s+locally\s+configured\s+ISID$$
  ^SPB\s+ISIS\s+Services\s+Info:$$
  ^\s+System$$
  ^\s+ISID\s+BVLAN\s+(Name\s+:\s+BMAC)\s+MCAST(T/R)\s+$$
  ^[-+\+]+\s*$$ -> Services

Services
  ^\*\s+${isid}\s+${bvlan}\s+${system_name}\s+\:\s+${system_bmac}\s*${multicast}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^ISIDs:\s+\d+
  ^. -> Error
